  "important_notes": [
    "ContentBasedRouter and Filter are @Incubating and live in debezium-scripting module (separate from core transforms in debezium-connect-plugins)",
    "ScriptingTransformation supports jsr223.* (Groovy, GraalJS) and wasm.* (Chicory/WebAssembly) engines",
    "ExtractNewRecordState.doApply() handles: tombstone, envelope validation, truncate, delete, insert/update flows with optional topic routing and field dropping",
    "DefaultDeleteHandlingStrategy implements 5 delete modes; REWRITE modes add __deleted header field",
    "SmtManager is a shared utility class used by all Debezium SMTs for record type validation",
    "ByLogicalTableRouter uses LRU caches for schema and topic regex results to improve performance",
    "ExtractChangedRecordState is intended to be chained BEFORE ExtractNewRecordState (with HeaderToValue in between)"
  ],

